rComments: One of the best Professors i have had to date. When she sees you connect with the material, Prof.Carney will go out of her way to help you.

Prof. Carney is a fabulous teacher, and her classes are truly a treasure. Instead of  the typical 'name, date, and title' approach to art history, it is refreshing to be taught CONTEXT, and therefore gain an understanding of art history is thorough. If you think she's a bad teacher it's because you don't really enjoy learning & have A.D.D.

Hi, I think that Prof. Carney is a wonderful and understanding teacher and mentor.  Anyone who has had the opportunity to speak with her personally will know this is the case.  She may be soft spoken but the woman knows what she is talking about!
